# ClinLang — Comprehensive Example
# Supports: core commands, symptoms with intensity+duration, extensions

# Patient demographics
pt 34M wt65 ht170

# Chief complaint
cc fever and productive cough 5 days

# History of presenting illness
hpi started with fever, then cough with yellow sputum, worsening SOB at rest

# Past medical history
pmh dm2 htn asthma

# Symptoms (intensity: + mild, ++ severe, +++ very severe | - improving, -- resolving)
# Duration appended after intensity: fever++3d means severe fever for 3 days

sx fever++3d cough++5d sob+ sweating+ chills-

# Vitals
vitals bp130/85 hr102 spo294 temp100.4 rr22

# --- EXTENSION COMMANDS (no core changes needed) ---

# Lab results
lab hb11.2 wbc14500 plt220000 crp48 esr65

# Chest X-Ray findings (exam)
exam crepitations+ consolidation+ bronchialbreathing+

# Diagnosis
dx community acquired pneumonia
